==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: făn chún xiāng jī
===Idiom===
'''[[反]][[唇]][[相]][[譏]]'''
# to make a sarcastic remark rather than submit another's criticism; to rebut with sarcastic remarks; to make a sarcastic comeback; to talk back
#: ''[[有]][[一次]]，[[我]][[看到]][[一]][[位]][[長者]][[在]][[買]][[菜]][[時]]，[[說]]:"[[你]][[這]][[菜]][[太]][[老]][[了]]!"[[賣]][[菜]][[者]][[立即]]'''反唇相譏''':"[[還有]][[你]][[老]][[啊]]!"''
#: ''One time, I saw an elderly person buying vegetables who said, "These vegetables of yours are too old!"  The vegetable seller immediately '''shot back''' with, "Well, you're old too!"''

